Put the signal in one file called 'signal.txt' and the driving in another called 'driving.txt'. 
Both files should be in format: "t x(t)\n" and the times in both files should match. 

Example:
'signal.txt'
0.010000 2.040512
0.020000 2.034066
0.030000 2.020611
0.040000 2.002333
0.050000 1.981134
0.060000 1.957674
...

'driving.txt'
0.010000 0.655922
0.020000 -0.078494
0.030000 -0.775742
0.040000 -0.474988
0.050000 -0.923393
0.060000 -0.065205
...
